completed: 2026-04-07
summary: |
  Fixed TaoshiBridge change detection. Replaced grow-only _seen_position_uuids set
  with hash-based _seen_positions dict that detects position updates (new orders,
  leverage changes). Signals now include signal_reason and order_count fields.
  Closed positions are pruned from tracking to prevent memory leaks.
  11 new unit tests covering all change detection scenarios.
